{"tid":1384624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家就算支持任何人 都唔好盲信佢地","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:56:14.000Z","uid":275921,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6fe38a862df04366547c3020243bd7d5c3e74b","tid":1384624,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"我知P牌講野一係負皮一係被block<br />\n但係我好想請大家做好精神武裝<br />\n唔好盲信任何人 天琦又好劉細良又好 任何KOL都係<br />\n<br />\n日本一萬円上面既日本幕末思想家 福澤諭吉講過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">先求一人之獨立 方有一國之獨立</span><br />\n所謂獨立 就係心理上唔依賴他人 能夠自己支配自己<br />\n例如自己能夠<span style=\"color: red;\">辨明事理 處置得宜</span> <br />\n就係<span style=\"color: red;\">不依賴他人智慧的獨立</span><br />\n<br />\n天琦為左香港 依家仍然身陷囹圄<br />\n劉細良既網台分析 可能有人會覺得好精僻<br />\n但係我覺得 佢哋講嘅都只可以當做一個觀點與角度<br />\n唔可以教條主義視之<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別當下不停吹風咁捧起劉細良 又有天琦既來信<br />\n大家更加要打醒精神 唔好盲信盲從<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後share多一段福澤諭吉《勸學篇》嘅內容：<br />\n<br />\n今天的愚人可以在明天變成智者，從前富強之國可以在現在淪於貧弱，古今這種例子是不少的。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 如果我們日本人從此立志求學，充實力量，先謀個人的獨立，再求一國的富強，則西洋人的勢力又何足懼？ 只須與講理者建交，對不講理者則驅除之。 這就是個人獨立和一國獨立的道理。</span><br />\n<br />\n依家正值危急存亡之秋 唔好鬆懈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99791537f449733baae6c6094690e9201f31452","tid":1384624,"uid":112433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"劉細良只係得個分析有用<br />\n行動黎講 要靠後生仔開創門路 <br />\n佢自己都講 只能夠share 到自己經驗<br />\n分析形勢可以參考 但行動要自創"},{"pid":"30748d9f10c829a3de19a1f44c260e2eb1f8f1cd","tid":1384624,"uid":215794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:27:47.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n佢地Day1講嘅嘢可能好啱<br />\n但Day2可能已經不適用<br />\nDay3又會修正返<br />\n<br />\n細良喺節目都會修正返之前講過嘅嘢<br />\n證明佢嘅團隊係有上網<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">亦都會改進</span>"},{"pid":"5e997cc49d13ca807d5b65355d12f4af95b94a42","tid":1384624,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得講得有道理既幫推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47a8778a7ec28cc54c5d6573a2fff15f86db46c","tid":1384624,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:32:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de22d9c33cc49ef214cf15eea93bc450ce1ae3e","tid":1384624,"uid":265060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7193a8ce5761940010498229f87db65721e57776","tid":1384624,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:41:02.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2f19d204f1a887a8b7fd3a805dc7b051e1a63e","tid":1384624,"uid":275921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}